Its the final version of surf_sunset made by Exither

ReadMe:

_______
Surf_sunset was made by Exither

Its a Skill-surf map with 6 Levels

There is one Bonus Level wich enables Jailkill

Also there are 6 secret Buttons (at every Level 1) to enable another secret in Jail

______
Special Thanks:

-I want to thank Sangre for all his help! Without him this map never would be get ready.

-Also I want to thank Bravesurf for his great help with the map.

-Thanks to all testers helping me to find bugs etc. 

-Last but not least I want to thanks to NLN-Team for helping me testing my map on their server.




I hope you enjoy surfing it and have fun!
